#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.trans"
msgstr "# triton.language.trans"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:4
msgid "根据dims参数转置张量的维度，不改变张量的数据，仅改变维度的顺序。专门优化的转置操作。"
msgstr "Transposes the dimensions of a tensor according to the `dims` parameter, without changing the tensor's data, only altering the order of the dimensions. A specially optimized transpose operation."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.trans(input, dims)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `input.trans(dims)` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.trans(input, dims)` - function call form\n"
"- `input.trans(dims)` - member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Features:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:12
msgid ""
"- 根据dims参数转置张量的维度\n"
"- 不改变张量的数据，仅改变维度的顺序\n"
"- 专门优化的转置操作\n"
msgstr ""
"- Transpose the dimensions of a tensor according to the `dims` parameter  \n"
"- Does not change the tensor's data, only reorders the dimensions  \n"
"- A specifically optimized transpose operation\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | 是 | 输入张量 |\n"
"| dims | List[int] | 是 | 转置后的维度顺序 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|----------------|------|----------|-------------|\n"
"| input | tensor | Yes | Input tensor |\n"
"| dims | List[int] | Yes | Dimension order after transposition |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 按照dims参数重新排列的维度\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 通过改变步长信息实现转置，无数据拷贝\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor\n"
"- **Shape:** dimensions rearranged according to the `dims` parameter\n"
"- **Data type:** same as the input tensor\n"
"- **Memory layout:** transposition achieved by modifying stride information, no data copy\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:24
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:26
msgid "- dims必须包含输入张量的所有维度索引"
msgstr "- dims must contain all dimension indices of the input tensor"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:28
msgid "### 2.2 DataType支持表"
msgstr "### 2.2 DataType Support Table"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/trans.md:30
msgid ""
"| 支持情况 | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|----------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU支持 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Support Status | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|----------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
